			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en"><span dir="auto">Camera Switching in Blueprints</span></h1>
			<div id="bodyContent">
				<div id="contentSub"><div id="mw-revision-info">Revision as of 21:44, 20 November 2014 by <a href="/User:AndrewHurley" title="User:AndrewHurley" class="mw-userlink">AndrewHurley</a>  <span class="mw-usertoollinks">(<a href="/index.php?title=User_talk:AndrewHurley&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="User talk:AndrewHurley (page does not exist)">Talk</a> | <a href="/Special:Contributions/AndrewHurley" title="Special:Contributions/AndrewHurley">contribs</a>)</span></div><br />
